<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Error - <%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="error-container">
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p class="error-message"><%= message %></p>

        <hr>
        <p class="error-hint">Oops! Something went wrong. But hey, at least it's not a kernel panic! </p>
        <p>If this problem persists, please contact support or try again later.</p>

        <a href="/" class="error-button">Go Back Home</a>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
